This paper discusses the challenge of making AI intelligible, which is a core topic in the field of AI (cs.AI). It also emphasizes the importance of developing new methods for explaining and controlling complex decisions, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the need for vocabulary alignment and interactive explanation, which are relevant to the field of computational linguistics (cs.CY).
